8struct nvkm_pll_vals;

10enum nv_clk_src {
11 nv_clk_src_crystal,
12 nv_clk_src_href,

14 nv_clk_src_hclk,
15 nv_clk_src_hclkm3,
16 nv_clk_src_hclkm3d2,
17 nv_clk_src_hclkm2d3, /* NVAA */

19 nv_clk_src_cclk, /* NVAA */
20
21 nv_clk_src_host,
22
23 nv_clk_src_sppll0,
24 nv_clk_src_sppll1,
25
26 nv_clk_src_mpllsrcref,
27 nv_clk_src_mpllsrc,
28 nv_clk_src_mpll,
29 nv_clk_src_mdiv,
30
31 nv_clk_src_core,
32 nv_clk_src_core_intm,
33 nv_clk_src_shader,
34

37 nv_clk_src_gpc,

39 nv_clk_src_hubk01,
40 nv_clk_src_hubk06,

43 nv_clk_src_daemon,
44 nv_clk_src_disp,
45 nv_clk_src_vdec,
46
47 nv_clk_src_dom6,
48
49 nv_clk_src_max,
50};
51
52struct nvkm_cstate {
53 struct list_head head;
54 u8 voltage;
55 u32 domain[nv_clk_src_max];
56};
57
58struct nvkm_pstate {
59 struct list_head head;
60 struct list_head list; /* c-states */
61 struct nvkm_cstate base;
62 u8 pstate;
63 u8 fanspeed;
64};
65
66struct nvkm_domain {
67 enum nv_clk_src name;
68 u8 bios; /* 0xff for none */
69#define NVKM_CLK_DOM_FLAG_CORE 0x01
70 u8 flags;
71 const char *mname;
72 int mdiv;
73};
74
75struct nvkm_clk {
76 const struct nvkm_clk_func *func;
77 struct nvkm_subdev subdev;
78
79 const struct nvkm_domain *domains;
80 struct nvkm_pstate bstate;
81
82 struct list_head states;
83 int state_nr;
84
85 struct work_struct work;
86#ifdef __NetBSD__
87 drm_waitqueue_t wait;
88 spinlock_t lock;
89#else
90 wait_queue_head_t wait;
91#endif
92 atomic_t waiting;
93
94 struct nvkm_notify pwrsrc_ntfy;
95 int pwrsrc;
96 int pstate; /* current */
97 int ustate_ac; /* user-requested (-1 disabled, -2 perfmon) */
98 int ustate_dc; /* user-requested (-1 disabled, -2 perfmon) */
99 int astate; /* perfmon adjustment (base) */
100 int tstate; /* thermal adjustment (max-) */
101 int dstate; /* display adjustment (min+) */
102
103 bool allow_reclock;
104
105 /*XXX: die, these are here *only* to support the completely
106 * bat-shit insane what-was-nouveau_hw.c code
107 */
108 int (*pll_calc)(struct nvkm_clk *, struct nvbios_pll *, int clk,
109 struct nvkm_pll_vals *pv);
110 int (*pll_prog)(struct nvkm_clk *, u32 reg1, struct nvkm_pll_vals *pv);
111};
112
113int nvkm_clk_read(struct nvkm_clk *, enum nv_clk_src);
114int nvkm_clk_ustate(struct nvkm_clk *, int req, int pwr);
115int nvkm_clk_astate(struct nvkm_clk *, int req, int rel, bool wait);
116int nvkm_clk_dstate(struct nvkm_clk *, int req, int rel);
117int nvkm_clk_tstate(struct nvkm_clk *, int req, int rel);
